

Get across the drawbridge and avoid
fireballs by ducking the high ones and
jumping over the low ones.  Raid the
dragon's treasures and escape using the
upper-left door.

                U  I  O
         move   J     L   move
                N  M  ,

    Press K to duck high fireballs
 Space / Button to jump low fireballs

0-9 * * * * * * * * * Select Difficulty

Esc * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * Pause

Ctrl-R* * * * * * * * * * * * * Restart

Ctrl-S* * * * * * * * * * *Toggle Sound
